properties.Name: LegalEntityBusinessMetric
properties.Description: The associated Business Metric reported by the Legal Entity for the indicated period.

Columns.Name: BusinessMetricId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a business metric.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated metric is calculated.

Columns.Name: LegalEntityBusinessMetricTargetValue
Columns.Description: The target value of the legal entity business metric for the indicated period.

Columns.Name: LegalEntityBusinessMetricValue
Columns.Description: The value of the legal entity business metric calculated for the indicated period.

Columns.Name: LegalEntityBusinessMetricNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the legal entity business metric.

Columns.Name: KeyPerformanceIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the metric is considered to be a key performance indicator during the given timeframe.
